text = "The Eternal City has at least one of these artificial stars as a light source.
Somehow, they figured out how to replicate the functions of a star really early on.
This idea of having an artificial sun was inspired by the lyrics
of Dirt Poor Robins' \"We Forgot We Were Human\"
By \"What do we need with the sun? Now we have an electric one\", 
they probably meant lightbulbs and not a literal electric sun,
but it's fun to interpret things differently."
